Aon Corp. (AON)  and  Zurich Financial
Services AG (ZURN)  have joined up with  WPP Plc (WPP) , the worldâ€™s biggest
advertising company, to offer global firms insurance policies
that would pay out to help restore tarnished reputations, the FT
reported, without attribution.  The policy will pay out up to $100 million for an annual
